{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":28805,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4772,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"害，道理确实是这样","timestamp":1592934348,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":28821,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":4772,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"虽然道理是对的，但这道理并不能推导出这个攻击……实际上一个对的道理价值很低，对的道理太多了","timestamp":1592934710,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":28901,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":4772,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"只要符合生产力水平，有什么欲望满足什么欲望，没毛病啊。上述婚制只要是双方法律地位平等我都不反对。","timestamp":1592940914,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":4772,"reply":3,"tag":null,"text":"台湾同性婚姻法律通过后，反对的群众开始攻击：下一步是不是开放一夫多妻/一妻多夫/多元成家/人和动物结婚。虽说是政治上故意偷换概念过度解读，但是道理倒是没错：人的欲望是无穷无尽的，世界上最可怕的就是人心。","timestamp":1592934225,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782582,"url":"","vote":{}}}